name: Blood Mountain
description:
This image was taken in Switzerland!


Camera: A7R3

There's something so majestic about mountains, and not just because of its sheer size and grandeur. Its sublimity is felt both in the macro and micro, reaching into the furthest, tiniest depths of your soul on a scale as large as stars. Like a supernova, it bursts from the earth and spreads across the soil like breaths on a cold day.
